4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:20:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9d15296b115e80f421999c2e9b02b5d1d91effb2","tid":1738950,"uid":118112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ce73502bcdf7f0641ccf82ee89cfc22371bdc0b","tid":1738950,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:39:03.000Z","msg":"咪嗌口號最好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:26:16.000Z","msg":"被攻入拘捕嗌唔嗌口號可以斟酌<br />\n或者直情剩係嗌&ldquo;留守無罪  濫捕無理&rdquo;<br />\n呢類冇政治訴求既野<br />\n講成自己一開始入校係見&ldquo;家人&rdquo;有難<br />\n要入去支援呢個屋企  呢類左膠野<br />\n記住鏡頭係影到有人丟汽油彈<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但佢未必認到係邊個</span><br />\n你就係要比人覺得果個人唔係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54bbc702dcf402f7ea70fca9c50f106457e2ff9e","tid":1738950,"uid":34751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T19:28:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13e0b355242ff4043688292a91306f824fee556e","tid":1738950,"uid":118112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:09:36.000Z","msg":"大家睇唔睇到<span style=\"color: red;\">許智峯</span>呀？<br />\n佢係<span style=\"color: orange;\">冇比人拉</span>地走呀<br />\n我相信poly入面仲有一百個<span style=\"color: red;\">許智峯</span><br />\n係<span style=\"color: orange;\">絕對冇參與暴動</span> 訓左幾晚 既<span style=\"color: navy;\">留守者</span>呀"},{"pid":"5383f2d83e5c4dd2cae0462ad022fb671d515460","tid":1738950,"uid":118112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:41:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足越早做越有利呀"}]}